{
  "texts": [
    "In order to see how narrow the topic of dynamic pricing in e-commerce is, we performed a search of articles covering pricing in general.",
    "The search conditions remained the same, namely a search field with the word \"pricing\" and its derivates, a time period and the WoS database.",
    "The search identified 82,557 papers from 1950 up to the present day.",
    "Following the same logic, we found 8645 papers dedicated to dynamic pricing (search expression \"dynamic NEAR/2 pricing\").",
    "According to the WoS database, researchers started to investigate dynamic pricing in 1968."
  ]
}